505
00:39:41.310 --> 00:39:46.290
Igual.

506
00:39:46.320 --> 00:39:47.370
Rachel!

507
00:39:55.190 --> 00:39:57.260
Rachel!

508
00:39:57.300 --> 00:39:58.350
Rachel!

509
00:40:09.540 --> 00:40:11.780
Rachel! Rachel!

510
